# Docker Mail Server - Email Aliases Configuration
# This file maps virtual email addresses to real mailboxes

## RFC 2142 Required Aliases
# These aliases are required by RFC 2142 for internet mail services
# https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc2142.html

# Postmaster - General mailbox for mail system issues
postmaster@antonshubin.com anton@antonshubin.com

# Abuse - Complaints about inappropriate public behavior  
abuse@antonshubin.com anton@antonshubin.com

# Hostmaster - DNS and domain administration
hostmaster@antonshubin.com anton@antonshubin.com

# Webmaster - Website administration
webmaster@antonshubin.com anton@antonshubin.com

